1
00:00:00,560 --> 00:00:02,000
If you’re hurt just say it.

2
00:00:02,480 --> 00:00:04,560
Is it that hard to be honest with your feelings?

3
00:00:05,680 --> 00:00:08,200
P’Pha, you came back to me.

4
00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:09,920
You really did.

5
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:14,920
I’m so fine.

6
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:16,560
Mark.

7
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:18,600
Who gave you that mark?

8
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:22,120
Shit!

9
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:25,200
Wait until that damn hickey’s gone then we can talk.

10
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:26,400
P’Kit.

11
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,600
How can I get rid of it.

12
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:39,280
Don’t scold me.
The more you get mad, the more I love you!

13
00:02:57,520 --> 00:03:03,120
My feelings for you are still the same.

14
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:13,040
Don’t scold me.
The more you get mad, the more I love you!

15
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:48,120
I forgot something. Can I go back up and get it?

16
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:58,520
No! Just leave it here!!!

17
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:35,880
That umbrella’s quite hard to close.
It needs some tricks… do you want my help?

18
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,200
Such a stubborn umbrella...

19
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:49,600
Just like its owner!

20
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:54,840
Such a stubborn umbrella. Just like its owner!

21
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,360
What is it?

22
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:18,240
If you don’t know why you’re here, then I’ll go back to sleep.

23
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,880
Wait.

24
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:22,000
Calm down.

25
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,960
Hmm...

26
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:26,520
Look closely.

27
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:29,200
There’s no hickey anymore.

28
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,400
So what? Why’re you showing it to me?

29
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:33,760
Let’s talk about us.

30
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:37,920
You said we’d talk if the hickey’s gone.

31
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:43,680
Are you sure? I can still see it.

32
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:52,000
I checked it very well earlier. It’s gone.

33
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:54,000
Are you blind?

34
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,960
Go back and check again.

35
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:01,560
My eyes might have a problem.

36
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:04,200
Guess, I need your help to check it for me.

37
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,760
I won’t do anything. I’ll go back to sleep.

38
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:08,360
Hey!

39
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,800
Get out of my bed.

40
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,960
Aw! Don’t be possessive.

41
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:26,000
We slept together here all night, didn’t we?

42
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,520
Aren’t you sleepy?

43
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:29,080
Come here. Let’s sleep together.

44
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,720
Do you want to try me?

45
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:33,680
What do you have for me to try?

46
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,800
Stop talking! You’re dead!

47
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,240
P’Kit.

48
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,760
Check again closely.

49
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:52,360
If it’s still there.

50
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:55,200
Or… are there any hickeys anywhere else?

51
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:58,880
Why?

52
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,880
Besides the one on your neck.

53
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:03,400
You also have other hickeys?

54
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,560
If I have any.

55
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:09,720
It must be only from you.

56
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:13,560
If you want a scar, I can give it to you.

57
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,960
So rough.

58
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:21,800
But I like it.

59
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,320
When you were gone.

60
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:28,320
I’ve been missing you all the time, you know?

61
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,120
Who are you?

62
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:33,760
Where is the real Mark?

63
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:39,480
The old Mark couldn’t win your heart and even lost you once.

64
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:42,720
So, I’ve changed to be a new man.

65
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:46,040
I’ll do everything I can when you’re still with me.

66
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:48,880
Because I don’t want to regret it.

67
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:51,840
Huh.

68
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:54,640
The new Mark’s so bold.

69
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,400
Aren’t you scared that I might beat you up?

70
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:00,480
Old or new me.

71
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:02,600
I’m always afraid of you.

72
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:04,520
But I have to be fearless.

73
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:06,560
Because I fear that you won’t love me.

74
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,760
Please give me a chance.

75
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:35,640
I didn’t want it to come out like that.

76
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:39,880
It’s my fault that I overstepped into someone else’s business.

77
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:46,520
While the only one I should care about is…

78
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,200
Are you still hurt?

79
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:01,320
Yes, I am.

80
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:05,880
It’s not easy to recover.

81
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:08,520
I need Dr. Kit to cure me.

82
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,200
P’Kit.

83
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,680
I’m sorry, Mark

84
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:29,440
and thank you for still having faith in me.

85
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,320
Mark.

86
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,000
What are you doing?

87
00:11:31,800 --> 00:11:33,440
Do you really want to know?

88
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:55,360
We aren’t together. You can’t do this to me.

89
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,400
I said you can’t.

90
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,680
I don’t like skipping steps.

91
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:16,280
Don’t scold me yet.

92
00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:18,360
I just…

93
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:31,240
I know how you think about me.

94
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:35,760
But I’m a good boy. I always listen to you.

95
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:40,000
If you tell me to stop, I will stop.

96
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:42,800
Even Though, I don’t want to.

97
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:09,240
You know that I can’t get over you.

98
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:13,080
It’s up to you now.

99
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:15,960
If you want to give me another chance.

100
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,920
I should be the one asking for a chance.

101
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:25,400
If we’re going to be boyfriends.

102
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:28,440
I should be the one who asks you.

103
00:13:29,040 --> 00:13:30,040
What?

104
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:32,720
Are you going to ask me?

105
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:40,680
Where? When? How?

106
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:43,760
Tell me more, Please!

107
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:45,600
Give me a clue!

108
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:48,160
You’ll know when it’s time.

109
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,120
Just be prepared.

110
00:13:51,160 --> 00:13:52,160
Can you ask me now?

111
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,200
Please!

112
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:56,600
This will be the last time for you to wait.

113
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:58,560
Can you do it?

114
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:01,080
Um.

115
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:05,800
I’ll wait, no matter how long.

116
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:08,120
Just one thing.

117
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,880
Please don't have me wait in vain.

118
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,720
I came today.

119
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:25,440
Because I won’t have much time for you next week.

120
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:29,680
I have to rehearse with Yu every evening.

121
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:33,960
For the Winter Love Festival. Did you know about this event?

122
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:36,040
That Music performance in the park, right?

123
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:40,840
Yes. You must go. I’ll book the front row for you.

124
00:14:41,160 --> 00:14:42,680
If I can, I will.

125
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:53,560
Don’t you want to know what I'm going to perform? And for whom?

126
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:56,680
If I want to know, I’ll ask Wayu myself.

127
00:14:57,640 --> 00:14:58,640
P’Kit.

128
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:02,680
This song will represent my feelings for you.

129
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:04,720
How can you ask about it from other people?

130
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:06,800
If that’s so.

131
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:10,320
You should go practicing now because I want to go back to sleep.

132
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,360
Wait.

133
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,720
I was wondering...

134
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,400
What now?

135
00:15:18,280 --> 00:15:21,920
If I come here next time as your boyfriend.

136
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:27,480
Then it won’t be skipping steps, right?

137
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:30,560
Enough! Get out!

138
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:43,080
So, I’m begging the stars to please tell me…

139
00:15:53,880 --> 00:15:55,560
I think I still need to adjust it.

140
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:57,320
It isn’t good enough.

141
00:15:58,120 --> 00:16:00,280
You’re even more serious than me.

142
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:04,440
And the song you prepared, is there something special about it?

143
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:07,000
Tell me.

144
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:11,920
I just picked one that goes along with yours.

145
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,200
Nah!

146
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:17,040
Don’t lie to me. I can tell when someone’s in love.

147
00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:20,120
And when you were singing.

148
00:16:20,160 --> 00:16:24,080
It made who you were thinking of.

149
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:29,360
Are you going to keep practicing?

150
00:16:29,520 --> 00:16:34,080
I give you 15 minutes more, then I’ll go.

151
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:36,480
We can continue tomorrow.

152
00:16:36,640 --> 00:16:39,880
I sing with my feelings and love.

153
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:42,040
So, it’ll come out beautiful anyhow.

154
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:43,880
Let’s pack our stuff.

155
00:16:55,760 --> 00:16:57,680
Where’s your mind at?

156
00:16:57,760 --> 00:16:59,000
Who’re you going to meet?

157
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:01,480
I…

158
00:17:02,920 --> 00:17:04,920
I’m going to see a friend. What’s so weird?

159
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:07,040
Don’t tell me that…

160
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:09,160
It’s this friend.

161
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:16,720
P’Thanu!

162
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:21,800
Are you looking for me? Do you need anything?

163
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:23,720
It’s Wayu.

164
00:17:23,839 --> 00:17:26,119
Ho! You didn’t get my joke.

165
00:17:26,839 --> 00:17:28,119
You didn’t pass the test.

166
00:17:29,360 --> 00:17:30,040
Mark.

167
00:17:31,280 --> 00:17:32,400
See you tomorrow.

168
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:35,760
I’ll treat him a dinner

169
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:38,040
to repay him for taking care of me when I was sick.

170
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:42,880
Let’s go, P’Thanu before it gets crowded.

171
00:17:43,560 --> 00:17:44,440
P’Thanu.

172
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:48,720
Don’t forget to watch him sing at the Winter Love Festival.

173
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:51,640
I tell you that it’ll be special.

174
00:17:53,040 --> 00:17:57,240
Uh. Don’t listen to him. He’s talking nonsense.

175
00:17:59,120 --> 00:17:59,920
Hey.

176
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:04,400
You need to hold on to him just to take him for dinner?

177
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:11,160
Well! Well!

178
00:18:16,160 --> 00:18:17,000
You!

179
00:18:17,520 --> 00:18:18,760
I’ll tell P’Kit!

180
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:47,560
I thought that we’d meet at the restaurant.

181
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:51,000
I just finished my drawing class around here,

182
00:18:51,080 --> 00:18:53,440
so we might as well go together.

183
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:56,160
Besides studying in Medicines,

184
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:59,560
I never knew that you’re also fond of drawing.

185
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:04,480
I learned it to use for note taking to help me understand difficult lessons better.

186
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:05,960
Now I’m taking a class.

187
00:19:06,040 --> 00:19:07,880
Because I want my drawings to look more realistic.

188
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:12,400
Can I see your drawings?

189
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:15,280
Sure. I’ll show you when we’re at the restaurant.

190
00:19:24,280 --> 00:19:26,040
Hey! What’s up, Thanu?

191
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:30,760
Why’re you here?

192
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:32,840
You told me that you’ll get back to study next semester, didn’t you?

193
00:19:33,840 --> 00:19:34,760
Aw!

194
00:19:35,800 --> 00:19:36,880
Nong Wayu.

195
00:19:40,360 --> 00:19:41,840
Did you guys come together?

196
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:46,200
Yes.

197
00:19:49,280 --> 00:19:50,280
Jack.

198
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:52,200
Nong Yu…

199
00:19:53,040 --> 00:19:57,120
Aw, Jack. You told me that it’d be only us.

200
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:59,040
Why is Wayu also here?

201
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:04,360
Are… you guys… having dinner together?

202
00:20:07,360 --> 00:20:08,960
We just need to discuss…

203
00:20:09,080 --> 00:20:11,360
about our competition.

204
00:20:12,320 --> 00:20:13,680
But it’s not a point.

205
00:20:15,040 --> 00:20:15,880
Koh.

206
00:20:16,320 --> 00:20:18,960
He didn’t come with me, but he came with Thanu.

207
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:19,840
Aw!

208
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:21,400
How could you, P’Thanu!

209
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:24,240
You came after and snatch him.

210
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:25,880
You break the rule.

211
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:28,120
Stop it, P’Jack and P’Koh.

212
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:30,840
I’m single now.

213
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:36,640
I can do anything anywhere with anyone whoever I want.

214
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,880
Besides.

215
00:20:40,320 --> 00:20:42,000
I’m the one who asked him out.

216
00:20:44,080 --> 00:20:45,080
Thanu.

217
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,640
I’ve never seen you liked anyone before.

218
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:51,680
And now you happen to be interested in someone I like.

219
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:54,560
What’re you trying to do?

220
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:56,840
You reap what others have sowed.

221
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:59,000
This isn’t right.

222
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:00,520
You guys are misunderstanding.

223
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:03,120
I came here today.

224
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:05,880
Because he wanted to repay my help previously.

225
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:07,720
It's still suspicious.

226
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:10,400
Nong Wayu’s so cute.

227
00:21:11,120 --> 00:21:12,960
You must have some kind of feelings for him.

228
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:14,040
That’s right.

229
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:17,440
You just use that excuse to smoothly get close to our Wayu.

230
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:19,800
And try to seduce him without his awareness.

231
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:22,480
That’s not going to work, P’Thanu.

232
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:23,960
Wait.

233
00:21:24,840 --> 00:21:25,840
We just…

234
00:21:26,760 --> 00:21:29,560
And since when did you guys become teammates?

235
00:21:30,280 --> 00:21:31,680
It’s useless to argue anyway.

236
00:21:32,840 --> 00:21:38,000
We all know that Wayu still can’t get over Parawee.

237
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:42,720
That’s in the past.

238
00:21:43,400 --> 00:21:44,400
But now.

239
00:21:49,080 --> 00:21:54,120
I believe that my love will help him forget his ex.

240
00:21:56,920 --> 00:21:58,640
No one can replace anyone, Jack.

241
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,240
Also,

242
00:22:00,800 --> 00:22:05,000
It’s better to let Wayu decide who he wants.

243
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:30,520
Thanks, again.

244
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,560
If you didn’t help me that day.

245
00:22:33,560 --> 00:22:34,640
I would be in trouble.

246
00:22:35,840 --> 00:22:36,640
And...

247
00:22:37,720 --> 00:22:39,040
I’m really sorry.

248
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:41,200
If...

249
00:22:41,320 --> 00:22:46,960
I said or did anything that seemed harassing you.

250
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:49,960
You feel better, right?

251
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:52,480
Take good care of yourself.

252
00:22:53,080 --> 00:22:54,240
It’s not only me.

253
00:22:55,280 --> 00:22:58,120
But also someone worried about you.

254
00:23:00,840 --> 00:23:01,840
And...

255
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:05,880
earlier, what you said about me and P’Pha.

256
00:23:06,560 --> 00:23:07,360
Well…

257
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:09,480
I want to tell you that...

258
00:23:17,840 --> 00:23:18,680
Wayu.

259
00:23:19,040 --> 00:23:21,320
You wanted to see my drawing, right?

260
00:23:31,600 --> 00:23:32,520
Whoa!

261
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:34,960
If I didn’t know that you’re studying in Medicine,

262
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:37,200
I’d think that you’re from the Faculty of Arts.

263
00:23:40,640 --> 00:23:44,280
You’re very talented, P’Thanu.

264
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:48,640
Wow.

265
00:23:49,120 --> 00:23:50,120
Kitty.

266
00:24:06,080 --> 00:24:08,880
Sorry! I spilt some water!

267
00:24:18,280 --> 00:24:20,240
Let me take care of P’Jack.

268
00:24:20,840 --> 00:24:21,720
There’s no need.

269
00:24:23,680 --> 00:24:24,520
P’Jack...

270
00:24:25,760 --> 00:24:27,400
keeps interrupting us.

271
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:29,680
I have an idea.

272
00:24:36,930 --> 00:24:40,520
