Both P’Jack and P’Koh will have to be disappointed, I suppose.

554
00:47:54,780 --> 00:47:56,040
They almost killed each other for Wayu.

555
00:47:56,340 --> 00:47:59,560
But suddenly someone else stole him.

556
00:48:00,450 --> 00:48:01,640
It’d be good if they can end up together.

557
00:48:05,180 --> 00:48:06,080
P’Padbok.

558
00:48:08,480 --> 00:48:10,600
Would you take a picture for me and...

559
00:48:11,310 --> 00:48:12,560
my boyfriend, please?

560
00:48:13,100 --> 00:48:14,320
What picture, Mark?

561
00:48:15,120 --> 00:48:16,680
I’m late for my class now.

562
00:48:17,290 --> 00:48:18,560
Maybe next time…

563
00:48:24,100 --> 00:48:25,160
Well, fine!

564
00:48:26,180 --> 00:48:29,720
I never refuse when people ask for help anyway.

565
00:48:39,630 --> 00:48:40,880
Give me some nice shots.

566
00:48:41,320 --> 00:48:44,040
I want to show everybody that...

567
00:48:44,700 --> 00:48:45,960
this man has been taken.

568
00:48:47,070 --> 00:48:48,440
I know.

569
00:48:49,610 --> 00:48:50,760
Despite my bad look,

570
00:48:51,280 --> 00:48:54,960
I don’t betray anyone, cold-bloodedly.

571
00:48:59,520 --> 00:49:00,320
Ready?

572
00:49:03,630 --> 00:49:06,720
I think P’Padbok probably misunderstood P’Thanu for something.

573
00:49:07,840 --> 00:49:09,440
You guys should calm down and talk.

574
00:49:13,680 --> 00:49:15,400
How good it is to be Thanu!

575
00:49:16,000 --> 00:49:18,200
People still protect you no matter how much bad you’ve done.

576
00:49:19,500 --> 00:49:20,570
Did he know...

577
00:49:21,470 --> 00:49:26,120
what his decent Thanu did to a bad guy like me?

578
00:49:27,500 --> 00:49:29,190
It’s our business.

579
00:49:30,000 --> 00:49:31,480
Don’t drag Wayu into this.

580
00:49:33,750 --> 00:49:35,280
I’m warning you.

581
00:49:36,440 --> 00:49:38,160
Don’t trust him too much.

582
00:49:39,030 --> 00:49:43,640
A guy like him never loves anyone but himself.

583
00:49:44,020 --> 00:49:45,640
He’s not what you said.

584
00:49:46,680 --> 00:49:49,920
How about a man who got away and left his friend behind?

585
00:49:50,570 --> 00:49:53,040
While his friend was waiting to be bailed out from the jail.

586
00:49:54,020 --> 00:49:55,240
What do you call a guy like that?

587
00:50:01,320 --> 00:50:04,520
I don’t know what happened between you guys.

588
00:50:05,740 --> 00:50:07,760
But if it happened with me and Mark.

589
00:50:09,080 --> 00:50:10,360
I’d trust my friend.

590
00:50:11,290 --> 00:50:13,040
Even if he left me waiting in the jail.

591
00:50:13,490 --> 00:50:14,490
I’d just wait.

592
00:50:15,560 --> 00:50:16,560
Because I know that...

593
00:50:16,920 --> 00:50:18,960
he’ll find a way to help me out.

594
00:50:20,600 --> 00:50:22,160
There won’t be anyone leaving another behind.

595
00:50:25,420 --> 00:50:27,280
Let me ask you, P’Padbok.

596
00:50:29,300 --> 00:50:32,240
Who’s actually betraying his friend’s trust.

597
00:50:32,800 --> 00:50:34,280
Don’t say anything if you don’t know!

598
00:50:34,310 --> 00:50:35,000
Stop already, Padbok!

599
00:50:36,440 --> 00:50:39,120
We can’t fix what happened that night.

600
00:50:39,960 --> 00:50:43,320
Tell me what I can do today to make it up.

601
00:50:45,680 --> 00:50:49,720
Do you think it’s that easy to recall our friendship that has been broken?

602
00:50:51,410 --> 00:50:52,120
Padbok!

603
00:50:53,520 --> 00:50:54,160
Padbok!

604
00:50:56,360 --> 00:50:58,160
What’s with you and Thanu again?

605
00:50:58,710 --> 00:50:59,920
Drop it now!

606
00:51:00,150 --> 00:51:02,280
We’re having a test. Hurry!

607
00:51:04,050 --> 00:51:05,880
Why does it have to be today?

608
00:51:06,600 --> 00:51:08,520
It’s for your own sake!

609
00:51:09,030 --> 00:51:10,320
Let’s go! Jack’s buying us time.

610
00:51:10,510 --> 00:51:12,000
Hurry! We need to run now.

611
00:51:15,280 --> 00:51:16,280
Remember.

612
00:51:16,920 --> 00:51:18,480
You can fool everyone today.

613
00:51:19,240 --> 00:51:21,880
But one day they’ll see how you actually are.

614
00:51:26,420 --> 00:51:27,240
Come on!

615
00:51:40,950 --> 00:51:41,800
I’m sorry.

616
00:51:42,740 --> 00:51:44,360
I shouldn’t bring you here.

617
00:51:46,110 --> 00:51:49,640
It’s my fault, I shouldn’t have got him here.

618
00:51:50,470 --> 00:51:51,680
It’s good that you’re aware of it.

619
00:51:52,190 --> 00:51:53,640
Be careful next time.

620
00:51:54,040 --> 00:51:56,240
Otherwise, I’ll consider you failing the probation.

621
00:52:00,000 --> 00:52:01,000
P’Thanu.

622
00:52:02,150 --> 00:52:03,280
Don’t make that face.

623
00:52:04,220 --> 00:52:05,600
You are not alone.

624
00:52:07,140 --> 00:52:08,320
I’m on your side.

625
00:52:09,960 --> 00:52:10,840
As well as P’Kit...

626
00:52:11,430 --> 00:52:12,280
and Mark.

627
00:52:17,110 --> 00:52:19,320
If P’Padbok tries to mess with you again.

628
00:52:19,890 --> 00:52:21,280
I’ll be your back up.

629
00:52:23,910 --> 00:52:25,840
What back up?

630
00:52:26,240 --> 00:52:28,800
You little shorty. If P’Thanu didn’t block him.

631
00:52:29,250 --> 00:52:31,360
You’d be beaten up already.

632
00:52:42,450 --> 00:52:43,450
Thanks for your faith in me.

633
00:52:44,510 --> 00:52:47,120
Let’s take a few more photos.

634
00:52:47,230 --> 00:52:47,960
Come on, P’Kit.

635
00:52:47,960 --> 00:52:48,960
What else to take?

636
00:52:49,380 --> 00:52:50,200
Come on, hurry up!

637
00:52:50,260 --> 00:52:51,440
You didn’t even…

638
00:52:59,840 --> 00:53:00,840
P’Thanu.

639
00:53:01,260 --> 00:53:02,260
Be honest with me.

640
00:53:03,270 --> 00:53:04,920
You’re taking care of Wayu...

641
00:53:05,670 --> 00:53:07,520
for Parawee.

642
00:53:08,350 --> 00:53:09,480
Am I right?

643
00:53:10,540 --> 00:53:12,320
Or you don’t approve of me doing this?

644
00:53:16,390 --> 00:53:19,800
If Wayu misunderstands your actions.

645
00:53:21,290 --> 00:53:23,560
how will you take care of his feelings?

646
00:53:26,920 --> 00:53:28,240
Wayu’s much better now.

647
00:53:28,970 --> 00:53:31,480
If Parawee’s back,

648
00:53:32,430 --> 00:53:34,200
I’ll make sure that...

649
00:53:34,760 --> 00:53:37,240
he won’t hurt Wayu once again.

650
00:53:37,310 --> 00:53:38,720
If he can’t do it.

651
00:53:40,060 --> 00:53:41,880
Will you take him back?

652
00:53:46,370 --> 00:53:47,880
I don’t have the right to do that.

653
00:53:50,900 --> 00:53:52,360
At first, I didn’t understand.

654
00:53:52,710 --> 00:53:54,960
Why Pha left Wayu with you.

655
00:53:56,170 --> 00:53:57,840
But now I can see that he knows that...

656
00:53:59,170 --> 00:54:02,320
you’ll never betray him...

657
00:54:03,120 --> 00:54:04,360
or cross the line with Wayu.

658
00:54:06,140 --> 00:54:09,840
But you can’t control the feelings.

659
00:54:12,660 --> 00:54:14,640
I want you to think this through.

660
00:54:22,710 --> 00:54:23,880
I’m begging you.

661
00:54:24,710 --> 00:54:26,240
Don’t pick a quarrel with Wayu again.

662
00:54:27,770 --> 00:54:29,160
I didn’t mean to.

663
00:54:30,260 --> 00:54:31,560
I just want him to...

664
00:54:32,470 --> 00:54:33,600
know the truth.

665
00:54:34,620 --> 00:54:35,760
So, he won’t be a fool...

666
00:54:36,870 --> 00:54:38,120
and take the wrong side.

667
00:54:39,010 --> 00:54:40,010
Isn’t it good, Jack?

668
00:54:41,040 --> 00:54:42,400
You’ll have less competitors as well.

669
00:54:44,400 --> 00:54:46,360
It’s not that he’d like me instantly.

670
00:54:46,710 --> 00:54:48,400
I want to win it fair and square.

671
00:54:49,790 --> 00:54:51,680
But what if what you were telling him...

672
00:54:52,050 --> 00:54:53,360
isn’t a real story?

673
00:54:57,430 --> 00:54:58,760
What do you mean?

674
00:55:00,380 --> 00:55:01,380
Well…

675
00:55:04,810 --> 00:55:08,120
Last time you said you’d only talk to Dr. Kit.

676
00:55:08,350 --> 00:55:11,200
Look how it turned out.

677
00:55:12,760 --> 00:55:13,960
It was a big deal.

678
00:55:14,450 --> 00:55:16,440
You should calm yourself down.

679
00:55:35,780 --> 00:55:37,280
Jew, hold him back!

680
00:55:37,980 --> 00:55:38,840
Jew!

681
00:55:39,510 --> 00:55:40,960
Let go of me!

682
00:55:41,320 --> 00:55:42,320
I cannot!

683
00:55:44,150 --> 00:55:45,150
Run Wayu! Run!

684
00:55:45,530 --> 00:55:46,120
Run!

685
00:55:47,000 --> 00:55:47,800
Where? Why, Jack?

686
00:55:47,910 --> 00:55:49,400
No time to explain! Hurry!

687
00:55:49,400 --> 00:55:50,400
Hey! P’Jack!

688
00:55:50,780 --> 00:55:51,360
P’Jack!

689
00:55:52,160 --> 00:55:52,680
P’Jack!

690
00:56:02,380 --> 00:56:04,680
Why is P’Padbok looking for me?

691
00:56:06,510 --> 00:56:07,680
It’s about Thanu.

692
00:56:08,360 --> 00:56:11,200
You screamed out to be on his side like that.

693
00:56:11,380 --> 00:56:12,560
So, Padbok got mad.

694
00:56:14,180 --> 00:56:15,440
Is that it?

695
00:56:16,040 --> 00:56:17,280
I’m not afraid of him.

696
00:56:17,490 --> 00:56:19,440
But I’m afraid.

697
00:56:20,040 --> 00:56:21,760
I can’t stand seeing you get hurt.

698
00:56:24,050 --> 00:56:25,050
Trust me,

699
00:56:25,680 --> 00:56:27,960
you’d better be here.

700
00:56:41,550 --> 00:56:42,720
Okay, it’s safe now.

701
00:56:44,510 --> 00:56:45,510
Nong… Nong Wayu?

702
00:56:54,140 --> 00:56:55,680
Are you looking for Wayu?

703
00:56:55,970 --> 00:56:56,560
Yes.

704
00:56:57,150 --> 00:56:57,960
Where is he?

705
00:57:04,470 --> 00:57:06,760
P’Padbok, what do you want from me?

706
00:57:07,790 --> 00:57:09,040
We haven’t finished.

707
00:57:10,230 --> 00:57:11,720
Thanu isn’t a good person like you think.

708
00:57:13,220 --> 00:57:15,080
Do you know why he dropped out?

709
00:57:16,450 --> 00:57:18,040
Besides betraying his friend,

710
00:57:18,110 --> 00:57:19,720
he has something worse.

711
00:57:20,910 --> 00:57:22,360
I don’t care.

712
00:57:22,470 --> 00:57:25,480
If he’s ready to tell me, he’ll tell me.

713
00:57:27,220 --> 00:57:29,000
Shut up and listen!

714
00:57:29,170 --> 00:57:31,840
That’s enough, Padbok! Let go of him now.

715
00:57:41,130 --> 00:57:42,440
Are you okay, Wayu?

716
00:57:44,120 --> 00:57:45,120
P’Thanu!

717
00:57:51,060 --> 00:57:52,440
I really want to know!

718
00:57:53,060 --> 00:57:53,920
Why?

719
00:57:55,350 --> 00:57:59,000
Why the friend I trust the most could do this to me?

720
00:57:59,660 --> 00:58:00,800
How could you leave me like that?

721
00:58:00,890 --> 00:58:01,890
I’ve never left you!

722
00:58:02,500 --> 00:58:03,520
Between you and me.

723
00:58:03,790 --> 00:58:05,960
Who’s the one betraying trust?

724
00:58:11,210 --> 00:58:13,200
Hey, don’t! You’ll get hurt.

725
00:58:13,680 --> 00:58:15,280
So, we’ll let them fight like this?

726
00:58:31,280 --> 00:58:33,160
I’m so done with you guys!

727
00:58:56,780 --> 00:58:58,160
This’s the first time you punched me.

728
00:59:00,300 --> 00:59:01,800
Your punch was harder than I thought.

729
00:59:44,090 --> 00:59:45,360
I’m sorry that...

730
00:59:47,040 --> 00:59:49,280
you got hurt because of me.

731
01:00:22,100 --> 01:00:28,440
Are you okay, Yu? I told you to be care…ful.

732
01:00:30,400 --> 01:00:31,400
I’m fine.

733
01:00:32,210 --> 01:00:33,440
P’Thanu saved me.

734
01:01:01,240 --> 01:01:03,440
What were you doing? I saw it.

735
01:01:06,360 --> 01:01:07,920
Hunnae!

736
01:01:07,920 --> 01:01:09,320
You blushed…

737
01:01:21,850 --> 01:01:22,850
Uhh, P’Kit.

738
01:01:23,890 --> 01:01:25,480
After what happened that day,

739
01:01:25,870 --> 01:01:29,050
P’Padbok got a serious warning from professors.

740
01:01:29,760 --> 01:01:31,200
How about the Medicine’s side?

741
01:01:31,240 --> 01:01:32,440
Did P’Thanu get any punishments?

742
01:01:32,770 --> 01:01:35,320
They got so bruised!

743
01:01:35,870 --> 01:01:36,870
Um...

744
01:01:37,330 --> 01:01:39,640
I saw P’Thanu got a warning, too.

745
01:01:40,850 --> 01:01:42,200
But no one asked for responsibility.

746
01:01:42,310 --> 01:01:43,480
So, it ended there.

747
01:01:43,770 --> 01:01:44,640
Um.

748
01:01:45,440 --> 01:01:47,200
Now I got why you warned me.

749
01:01:47,540 --> 01:01:50,720
Violence never fixed any problems.

750
01:01:51,500 --> 01:01:55,920
No idea when they’re going to settle eventually.

751
01:01:57,350 --> 01:01:58,440
You wanna help them?

752
01:01:59,140 --> 01:02:00,440
You’re good at making up, aren’t you?

753
01:02:01,740 --> 01:02:02,740
Well…

754
01:02:03,320 --> 01:02:04,800
I have to be good at it,

755
01:02:05,110 --> 01:02:06,520
since my boyfriend gets mad easily.

756
01:02:06,570 --> 01:02:07,720
Who got mad easily?

757
01:02:07,790 --> 01:02:10,640
I saw you quite like it.

758
01:02:10,850 --> 01:02:12,360
So, should I give you some more treats?

759
01:02:12,540 --> 01:02:13,880
I’ll serve you three times...

760
01:02:13,990 --> 01:02:14,990
before and after meals every day.

761
01:02:20,790 --> 01:02:23,560
I think we should practice diagnosing.

762
01:02:24,180 --> 01:02:25,320
Put it on, Doctor.

763
01:02:29,720 --> 01:02:32,960
From my conditions.

764
01:02:33,180 --> 01:02:36,000
What do you think, Dr. Kamjornkij?

765
01:02:36,050 --> 01:02:37,960
Am I having lovesickness or...

766
01:02:38,410 --> 01:02:41,360
broken heart from missing someone too much?

767
01:02:48,590 --> 01:02:49,590
I’m sorry, sir.

768
01:02:50,270 --> 01:02:53,160
You only have 5 minutes and 59 seconds left to live.

769
01:02:53,520 --> 01:02:55,600
If you have anything you want to do, do it now.

770
01:02:57,470 --> 01:02:59,080
Cursing me like this...

771
01:02:59,440 --> 01:03:01,600
aren’t you afraid of becoming a widower even before graduating?

772
01:03:03,260 --> 01:03:04,720
I think this stethoscope is...

773
01:03:05,640 --> 01:03:06,480
broken.

774
01:03:06,990 --> 01:03:07,680
Better use this one.

775
01:03:07,680 --> 01:03:08,280
Hey!

776
01:03:09,680 --> 01:03:11,880
So, who’s the one studying Medicine?

777
01:03:14,470 --> 01:03:18,040
What a mean doctor! You have to console me.

778
01:03:18,410 --> 01:03:21,840
My heart is extremely weak.

779
01:03:22,800 --> 01:03:25,320
Do you have any way to help?

780
01:03:25,540 --> 01:03:26,540
I need...

781
01:03:27,690 --> 01:03:28,880
something strong.

782
01:03:29,210 --> 01:03:30,400
Very very strong!

783
01:03:30,730 --> 01:03:33,720
Hmm. Let me give you something refreshing?

784
01:03:33,820 --> 01:03:34,720
Um.

785
01:03:37,420 --> 01:03:38,200
Try this.

786
01:03:38,370 --> 01:03:41,680
Jelly Vitamin A-Z. It has all the vitamins.

787
01:03:41,790 --> 01:03:46,040
Since A B1 B2 B3 B5 B6 B7

788
01:03:47,530 --> 01:03:48,530
Okay.

789
01:03:49,210 --> 01:03:50,210
fine…

790
01:03:50,470 --> 01:03:51,470
Refreshing is fine.

791
01:03:52,020 --> 01:03:53,560
Instead of obsessing with dirty stuff.

792
01:03:54,090 --> 01:03:55,440
You should worry about Wayu!

793
01:03:59,250 --> 01:04:00,920
Why do I have to worry about him?

794
01:04:01,470 --> 01:04:02,880
From what I told you.

795
01:04:03,500 --> 01:04:07,000
Don’t you think Wayu and P’Thanu are very happy now?

796
01:04:08,210 --> 01:04:09,360
Or did you know something?

797
01:04:12,200 --> 01:04:13,200
P’Thanu.

798
01:04:13,490 --> 01:04:15,040
Be honest with me.

799
01:04:15,470 --> 01:04:19,720
You’re taking care of Wayu for Parawee.

800
01:04:20,480 --> 01:04:21,880
Am I right?

801
01:04:24,170 --> 01:04:25,880
He’s a serious person.

802
01:04:26,640 --> 01:04:29,880
If he’s really into Wayu, we’ll see.

803
01:04:31,420 --> 01:04:32,030
P’Kit.

804
01:04:33,220 --> 01:04:34,640
Are you hiding something from me?

805
01:04:35,490 --> 01:04:38,600
Didn’t you say that I’m the most important person?

806
01:04:43,510 --> 01:04:44,760
At first, I didn’t understand.

807
01:04:45,700 --> 01:04:48,080
Why Pah would leave Wayu with you.

808
01:04:49,470 --> 01:04:50,850
But now I can see that...

809
01:04:52,170 --> 01:04:55,320
he knows that you’ll never betray him...

810
01:04:56,180 --> 01:04:57,560
or cross the line with Wayu.

811
01:04:59,160 --> 01:05:00,760
I know as much as I can see!

812
01:05:04,480 --> 01:05:05,320
Mark.

813
01:05:09,150 --> 01:05:10,760
Do you have any plans tonight?

814
01:05:11,780 --> 01:05:12,560
Hmmm.

815
01:05:13,740 --> 01:05:15,160
You changed the subject.

816
01:05:16,380 --> 01:05:17,380
Are you asking me out?

817
01:05:19,120 --> 01:05:20,480
You wanna sleep over at my room?

818
01:05:24,440 --> 01:05:25,440
What did you just say?

819
01:05:26,750 --> 01:05:28,960
You wanna sleep over at my room?

820
01:05:32,430 --> 01:05:33,430
What did you say?

821
01:05:33,700 --> 01:05:35,480
Are you going to sleep at my room tonight?!

822
01:05:50,450 --> 01:05:52,520
Should’ve let you sleep on the floor.

823
01:06:15,460 --> 01:06:17,080
I’m a sleep-cuddler.

824
01:06:19,710 --> 01:06:21,400
I’m also a sleep-elbower!

825
01:06:24,600 --> 01:06:25,000
Hey.

